rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg001
rows.name:
Hey, Yuou, is this really the
place for a strategy meeting?

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg002
rows.name:
Uh, you want to have a strategy
meeting in a place like this, Yuou?

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg003
rows.name:
Yuou, do you really expect us to
hold a strategy meeting here?

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg004
rows.name:
Hey, Yuou. Are you really planning
on having a strategy meeting here?

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg005
rows.name:
I thought perhaps it would be nice
to have a change of scenery.

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg006
rows.name:
Now, let's start off by considering
our past battle experiences.

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg007
rows.name:
Having analyzed our battles thus far,
I've come to a conclusion.

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg008
rows.name:
Considering we have five Drivers
on our team, we ought to think
more about our formation.

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg009
rows.name: Tora get it.

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg010
rows.name:
Tora so busy working with Hana,
not have time to think about teamwork
with boss and friends!

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg011
rows.name:
Indeed. Synergy between Blades
and Drivers is important, but it can
only get you so far.

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg012
rows.name:
Yuou saying we should think about
synergy between Driver and Driver?

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg014
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ]Wh-what... What is that,
over on the other table?!

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg015
rows.name: [ML:Feeling ]Meh-meh? What wrong with Yuou?

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg016
rows.name: Hmm? Ah, no, it's nothing.

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg017
rows.name:
As I was saying, we must consider the
importance of the Driver's actions in
co-ordination with-

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg018
rows.name: Wha?!

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg019
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ]That woman over there... She's...
She's eating a dessert I've never
seen before!

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg020
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ]It looked like some kind of sweet
pastry, but it contained...

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg101
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Think ]Fruit?!

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg021
rows.name: What should I say?

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg022
rows.name: Is that woman distracting you?

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg023
rows.name: Is our current teamwork that messy?

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg024
rows.name: What should I say?

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg025
rows.name: Is that woman distracting you?

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg026
rows.name: Is our strategy just that awful?

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg027
rows.name: What would be the best thing to say?

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg028
rows.name: The woman over there distracts you?

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg029
rows.name: Is our current strategy that flawed?

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg030
rows.name: What should I say to him?

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg031
rows.name: Is that woman distracting you?

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg032
rows.name: Is our teamwork that lousy?

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg033
rows.name:
No...no, it's nothing. There's no
need to concern yourselves.

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg034
rows.name: Yuou really staring a lot though!

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg102
rows.name:
But Tora maybe notice same thing
Yuou notice.

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg035
rows.name:
Tora have feeling Tora seen
that lady somewhere before.

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg036
rows.name: Maybe she spy following us?!

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg037
rows.name:
No, really, that's really not the case!
She has nothing to do with this.

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg038
rows.name: Meh-meh?

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg039
rows.name: Then what's wrong?

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg040
rows.name: So what's the deal?

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg041
rows.name: Then what is the matter?

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg042
rows.name: So what're you staring for?

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg043
rows.name: It's...the dessert.

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg044
rows.name: Dessert? What Yuou mean?

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg045
rows.name:
I...I couldn't help noticing the
dessert that woman was eating.

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg046
rows.name:
What, that all? Yuou should have said
earlier!

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg047
rows.name:
Tora want to eat scrummy food too!
We all order dessert now?!

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg048
rows.name: All right, all right.

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg049
rows.name:
Why don't we all discuss our battle
plans over some dessert?

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg050
rows.name: All right already.

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg051
rows.name:
Why don't we all discuss our battle
plans over some dessert?

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg052
rows.name: You leave me no choice.

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg053
rows.name:
We will simply have to order dessert
and eat as we discuss our strategies.

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg054
rows.name: All right, we get it.

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg055
rows.name:
Why don't we all discuss our battle
strategies over some dessert?

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg056
rows.name:
In that case, I'll have three of what
she's having. If you're okay with that.

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg057
rows.name: (REMOVED)

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg058
rows.name: Ah, no, it's nothing like that...

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg059
rows.name: It wasn't any of your fault, I was just-

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg060
rows.name: Ahhhh!

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg061
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ]I knew it!
It is indeed a fruit filling!

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg062
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ]And bathed in some liquid, no less...
but what is it? Honey?! Fruit juice?!

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg063
rows.name: [ML:Feeling ]What is Yuou doing?

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg064
rows.name: Mmmmmwhat?

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg065
rows.name:
Oh, my apologies.
Where were we again?

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg066
rows.name:
Ah yes, I have a proposition. I suggest
in future, we arrange our units as
follows, so that-

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg067
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Think ]Oh, my word!

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg068
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ]Can it be true? There is something
more than just fruit contained within
that crispy exterior?

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg069
rows.name: [ML:Feeling ]It's...it's cream!

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg070
rows.name: But what kind of cream?

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg071
rows.name:
Gaaah, I can't take it any longer! I must
know what kind of cream they're using!

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg072
rows.name: Uh... Yuou?

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg073
rows.name: Uh... Yuou?

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg074
rows.name: Excuse me... Yuou?

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg075
rows.name: Err... Yuou?

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg076
rows.name: What?!

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg077
rows.name:
Oh, I'm very sorry. Er... Now about our
strategy...

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg078
rows.name: That not problem here.

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg079
rows.name:
What Yuou say in mind, Yuou actually
say in mouth. We hear everything.

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg080
rows.name: Y-you heard all that?!

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg081
rows.name:
Silly Yuou. If Yuou want dessert so
badly, Yuou should just say!

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg082
rows.name: No - but - I - ahh...

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg083
rows.name:
It all fine. Tora want to eat tasty
yumyums too!

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg084
rows.name: That okay, everyone?

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg085
rows.name:
Sure, sure. What is it you wanted to
order, Yuou?

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg086
rows.name:
I'm on board with that. Whatcha
wanna eat, Yuou?

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg087
rows.name:
I suppose there's nothing else for it.
What would you like to eat, Yuou?

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg088
rows.name:
I suppose I'm up for that. What d'you
want to order, Yuou?

rows.label: kizunatalk059_msg089
rows.name:
Well... In that case, I'll have three of
what that woman's having!
